parameters.description: Log intrinsic growth rate of Crown-of-Thorns starfish (log(year^-1)); initial guess from expert opinion.
Log carrying capacity of starfish (log(individuals/m2)); estimated from historical outbreak data.
Log predation rate impacting slow-growing corals (log(rate)); derived from observed coral decline rates.
Log predation rate impacting fast-growing corals (log(rate)); derived from observed coral decline rates.
Efficiency of predation by starfish (unitless, between 0 and 1); estimated from ecological experiments.
Coefficient for sea-surface temperature effect on starfish growth (unitless); set to 0 as placeholder.
Log standard deviation for starfish observation error (log(individuals/m2)); prevents numerical issues.
Log standard deviation for slow coral observation error (log(%)); prevents numerical issues.
Log standard deviation for fast coral observation error (log(%)); prevents numerical issues.
